OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright and
OL,6,Fsunny end to the day for most. A fine
OL,7,Fnight with clear skies to follow
OL,8,Facross the region. Chance of mist
OL,9,Fpatches developing later in the night
OL,10,Fas the wind remains light. Feeling
OL,11,Fwarm overnight for many.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FBright and sunny, becoming
OL,14,Fvery hot for most by afternoon, the
OL,15,Fsunshine may turn a little hazy due to
OL,16,Fhigh-level cloud later. Cooler near
OL,17,Fcoasts and winds remaining light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
