OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FRemaining
OL,6,Fmostly dry, sunny and hot throughout.
OL,7,FIsolated thunderstorms possible at
OL,8,Ftimes. Freshening north-easterly winds
OL,9,Fdeveloping by Saturday, strong across
OL,10,Fparts of the region by Sunday.
OL,11,FTemperatures well above average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
